item.title: US Stocks Picked
item.description: AGNC (AGNC Investment Corp.) Small AGNC Investment (AGNC) and MPLX are favorable investment options, considering the active portfolio-management strategy, decent liquidity, attractive ROE, and potential for continued growth in payouts. CSCO (Cisco Systems, Inc.) Mega Cisco Systems shows promise for future growth with its focus on sustainability, dividend payments, and potential in the 5G networks market, but it also faces risks from emerging technologies and market volatility.
